Hours.description: Integer data that represents the data sample time stamp hours.

Minutes.description: Integer data that represents the data sample time stamp minutes

Seconds.description: Integer data that represents the data sample time stamp seconds.

Humidity.description: Floating point data that represents the relative humidity

Temperature.description: Floating point data that represents temperature in degrees Fahrenheit.

Pressure.description: Floating point data that represents pressure in kilo-Pascals (kPa).
